    "However, around 2017, both curves show a shift in trend, namely a vast increase in publications highlighting the interest and potential prospects of artificial intelligence and its subtopics for a variety of applications.Due to the rapid growth [21] of research in the field of deep learning (see Fig. 1a), we provide an overview of the various deep learning methodologies in deterministic computational mechanics.",
    "To limit the scope of this work, we focus on deterministic approaches and problems within computational mechanics.",
